{"tid":151403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開][外國連登仔]Shia LaBeouf扯旗反Donald Trump比4chan計角度成功拆旗","createTime":"2017-03-10T20:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T05:47:15.000Z","uid":916,"like":95,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"841e0f14e773f0ac5cb5a8ae40eaeb97a5523273","tid":151403,"uid":916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T20:05:08.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 岩岩個post柒左一鑊所以開多個post廢事個標題誤導人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/151385/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/151385/page/1</a><br />\n原post, 要笑我係呢個post笑我好la<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw, He will not divide us 係Shia LaBeouf ge反trump 裝置藝術計劃<br />\n<br />\n正文：<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://getriced.com/will-not-divide-us-capture-flag-edition/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgetriced.com%2Fwill-not-divide-us-capture-flag-edition%2F&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=449858b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://getriced.com/will-not-divide-us-capture-flag-edition/</a> (我搵唔到4chan個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n話說外國有個撐trump嘅人叫Shia LaBeouf, 佢打算係一個冇人知嘅地方扯枝旗寫住&quot;He will not divide us&quot;黎反Trump, 仲整左個youtube live<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/760S26k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F760S26k.png&h=087dbad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n心諗, 個背景乜都冇實冇死la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點都估唔到, 4chan一班痴線佬靠飛機黎定位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/84z4HT3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F84z4HT3.jpg&h=f5ae3b58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s8275u8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs8275u8.jpg&h=054f6d2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n得到大約位置後有人立即揸車到附近位置響安嘗試令個cam收到音, 成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VA238LD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVA238LD.jpg&h=4da30793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但佢地依然唔滿足, 於是開始計星星位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2g2be9j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2g2be9j.jpg&h=685b6a6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjd7Sf4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkjd7Sf4.jpg&h=f42f2d6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後真係有人搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲幫佢換左trump頂帽同一件pepe嘅t shirt<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W3811a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW3811a5.jpg&h=570ea1ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Ej7Np9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Ej7Np9.gif&h=7bb39f3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成個過程只係用左37個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後admin都投降鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http