ia at a diner in Greenville, Tennessee</span>, although some in the thread still believed the flag was in the Great Lakes area due to wind patterns. The time of the sunset in Greenville matched with the time of sunset on the stream, and so did the weather on local weather reports.<br />\n<br />\n4channers began looking into flight patterns. One of the few clues available on the stream were the contrails left by airplanes. Greenville was finally confirmed as the location after two planes observed on online flight radars intersected over the town and were seen on the stream.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://heatst.com/tech/he-will-not-divide-us-livestream-placed-in-middle-of-nowhere-but-4chan-still-found-way-to-troll-it/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheatst.com%2Ftech%2Fhe-will-not-divide-us-livestream-placed-in-middle-of-nowhere-but-4chan-still-found-way-to-troll-it%2F&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=d897ea7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://heatst.com/tech/he-will-not-divide-us-livestream-placed-in-middle-of-nowhere-but-4chan-still-found-way-to-troll-it/</a>"},{"pid":"11edc0562b0b652be45f4a30888316d84ef1fa10","tid":151403,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T05:22:17.000Z","msg":"人地4chan耐過連登仔幾耐<br />\n咪影衰人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f54b14d64a7e7603021b500aff5c5d7bd6fa928","tid":151403,"uid":37933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T05:24:51.000Z","msg":"自己睇左段新聞<br />\n件事類似係左膠Shia想直播枝旗反Trump<br />\n本身幾個public location都俾人拆左落黎<br />\n跟住就轉左去空地到播 仲話你地今次無可能拆到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟手4chan就睇陽光倒影睇飛機睇星估到大概係邊 再叫人係個範圍到揸車響再睇住直播睇下有冇聲出黎估實際位置 最後拆撚左枝旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個case未必關政治事<br />\n反而似果d幅相我加密左你破唔倒架啦<br />\n跟手唔夠3秒俾人破左d柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78cbb616e5c1afc647a47